{
  "texts": [
    "A Short Primer on LLMs While LLMs like ChatGPT are accessible to those without a background in computer science, researchers must understand the basics of these research tools.",
    "LLMs were made possible by massive amounts of text data that have become available in recent years.",
    "Largescale digitization projects aimed at the world's biggest archives and libraries have produced abundant digital texts.",
    "Simultaneously, the 21 st century has ushered in a golden age of natively produced digital text; from social media to close captioning of debates to community announcements and newsletters.",
    "In addition to the accumulation of text data, the development of more advanced hardware and improved software and architecture for storing data."
  ]
}